c   carrier      127 25  25  2   -   60  60   3  127  -    -    4

       A carrier is like a mobile airfield. It is the only ship that planes
may land on (although other ships may carry and launch them). A carrier
should probobly also be escorted, as the cargo of planes makes it a
likely target.

